<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=107102.msg976780#msg976780" rel="nofollow">Re: 【GM手册-规则篇】4.战斗规则</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_976780'));undefined;">繁</a>
